for i in range(int(input())):
    a = input()
    b = input()
    s = sorted(a)
    k = sorted(b)
    p1 = 0
    p2 = 0
    c = 0
    while p1 < len(a) and p2 < len(b):
        if s[p1] == k[p2]:
            p1 += 1
            p2 += 1
            c += 1
        elif s[p1] > k[p2]:
            p2 += 1
        elif s[p1] < k[p2]:
            p1 += 1
    print(c)
